<br>
Also on his mask was a star and moon design, also the face piece was outlined with obsidion, along with the two eye slits. His chest plate was dark silver and decorated with a moon, stars, and clouds, and the chest plate extended on the solders for protection... His sleeves and pants were dark purple velvet, and mixed in with chain link.  <br>
<br>
